: : Rodimus Prime : :

Rodimus hadn't taken his eyes off of Nightlight. He just stood, 
waiting for her proframming to be restored, for his wife to come back 
to him. He is brought out of his trance by the cribs signal. Elita 
was awake.

Rodimus Prime: Azure, Yggdrasil, excuse me. I'll be right back, Elita 
has just woken up.

Rodimus heads to his quarters, where he finds Elita in the crib. He 
picks her up.

Rodimus Prime: Hello there, lil' one. Let's take a little walk. I'll 
get you some energon and food at the mess hall, and then maybe mommy 
will be back by then.

Roddy walks out going to the mess hall. This gave Elita a new chance 
to look around new areas of the ship.
